@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam stateFontSize 14
skinparam arrowFontSize 12

title Диаграмма состояний ParserCoordinatorActor

[*] --> IDLE

IDLE --> WAITING_FOR_DOCUMENT : ParseDocumentRequest\n/ tell(ReadDocumentRequest) → Reader

WAITING_FOR_DOCUMENT --> BUILDING_SUBTREES : DocumentLoaded\n/ segment root entity\n/ tell(BuildSubtreeRequest) × N → Workers

BUILDING_SUBTREES --> BUILDING_SUBTREES : SubtreeCompleted [pending > 0]\n/ store subtree result

BUILDING_SUBTREES --> COMPLETED : SubtreeCompleted [all received]\n/ assemble AstDocument\n/ tell(ParseCompleted) → Collector

COMPLETED --> [*]

note right of BUILDING_SUBTREES
  Fan-out: N сегментов отправлены
  N worker-акторам. Координатор
  ожидает N ответов SubtreeCompleted.

  Сегменты распределяются round-robin:
  worker_index = segment_index % worker_count
end note

@enduml
